        {
            "title": "訪問旅遊達人小斯｜$1.3億入市北角新盤係「智商稅」？買樓投資關鍵考慮咩因素？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><div class=\"aspect-[16/9] size-full overflow-hidden rounded-lg object-cover mb-module-gap\"></div></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E9%81%94%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8F%E6%96%AF%EF%BD%9C13%E5%84%84%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%A4%E4%BF%82%E3%80%8C%E6%99%BA%E5%95%86%E7%A8%85%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9F%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%92%A9%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%9F-113319091.html",
